WEBVTT

00:05.999 --> 00:11.740
I like Samsung because it's new and it's always the latest, greatest thing.

00:12.355 --> 00:16.677
I love taking pictures and putting them on my social channels...

00:16.775 --> 00:18.111
...and just sending them to my friends.

00:18.245 --> 00:21.969
I have my feed and it comes up with all the music that I listen to...

00:22.078 --> 00:23.405
...and the clothes that I wear.

00:23.550 --> 00:27.601
All the latest news in fashion shows and sales going on in New York.

00:27.681 --> 00:29.153
It's like, that's crazy.

00:29.710 --> 00:31.144
The world's at your fingertips.

00:31.235 --> 00:32.577
That's the way I see it.

